'''馬克·R·查爾斯'''（{{lang-en|Mark R. Charles}}）是一名[[美國原住民|美國原住民]]出身的維權人士、公共發言人、顧問和作家<ref>{{cite book | author = Mark Charles and Soong-Chan Rah | title = Unsettling Truths The Ongoing, Dehumanizing Legacy of the Doctrine of Discovery | publisher = InterVarsity Press | year = 2019 | url = https://www.ivpress.com/unsettling-truths | access-date = 2020-09-10 | archive-date = 2020-10-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017195232/https://www.ivpress.com/unsettling-truths | dead-url = no }}</ref>，以及記者、博客、[[加爾文主義|改革]]牧師和[[程序員|程序員]]<ref name="Silliman2020">{{cite web |last1=Silliman |first1=Daniel |title=For Third-Party Christians, Some Things Are More Important Than Winning |url=https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2020/july-august/evangelical-third-party-voter-candidate-president-election-.html |publisher=[[Christianity_Today|Christianity Today]] |language=en |date=22 June 2020 |access-date=2020-09-10 |archive-date=2020-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623101236/https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2020/july-august/evangelical-third-party-voter-candidate-president-election-.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=speaker>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abqjournal.com/16822/1025am-navajo-speaker-calls-for-51st-virtual-state.html|title=10:25am -- Navajo Speaker Calls for '51st Virtual State'|author=ABQJournal News Staff|date=April 13, 2009|website=[[Albuquerque_Journal|Albuquerque Journal]]|access-date=2020-09-10|archive-date=2019-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725202048/https://www.abqjournal.com/16822/1025am-navajo-speaker-calls-for-51st-virtual-state.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也是[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]的[[無黨籍|無黨籍]]候選人<ref name=running>Bennett-Begaye, (May 30, 2019). Jourdan {{Cite web|url=https://newsmaven.io/indiancountrytoday/news/yá-át-tééh-i-am-running-for-president-qkbih7f1lkyAFcvN7x6LDw/|title='Yá'át'tééh ... I am running for president'|website=[[Indian_Country_Today|IndianCountryToday]].com|access-date=2022-03-09|archive-date=2019-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725205400/https://newsmaven.io/indiancountrytoday/news/y%C3%A1-%C3%A1t-t%C3%A9%C3%A9h-i-am-running-for-president-qkbih7f1lkyAFcvN7x6LDw/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==早年生活==
查爾斯的父親是[[納瓦霍人|納瓦霍人]]，母親是[[荷兰裔美国人|荷兰裔美国人]]，在{{le|蓋洛普 (新墨西哥州)|Gallup, New Mexico|新墨西哥州蓋洛普}}成長<ref name=speaker/><ref name=member>{{Cite web|url=https://www.knau.org/post/member-navajo-nation-announces-us-presidential-campaign|title=Member of Navajo Nation Announces U.S. Presidential Campaign|first=Ryan|last=Heinsius|date=May 31, 2019|website=[[KNAU|KNAU]]|access-date=2020-09-10|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111190111/https://www.knau.org/post/member-navajo-nation-announces-us-presidential-campaign|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在[[加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校|加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校]]畢業<ref name=speaker/>。

